data.name: lbl_writeDirection.Text
data.value: Directions: You have 20 minutes to plan and write your response. Your response will be judged on the basis of the quality of your writing and on how well your response presents in the lecture and their relationship to the reading passage. Typically, an effective response will be 150 to 225 words. Question: Summarize the points made in the lecture, being sure to explain how they cast doubt on specific points made in the reading passage.
